    <section class="space-y-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-cyan-500/40 bg-cyan-500/10 px-5 py-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-200 shadow-glow animate-float-slow" data-parallax-depth="0.12">
        <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
        <span>Engineering Signal v2.0</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gradient sm:text-6xl">
        Designing luminous systems for teams who keep the world moving.
      </h1>

      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
        I'm Dave Hulbert — an engineering leader crafting human-centred, resilient platforms. I connect AI strategy, organisational design, and dependable software delivery so ambitious teams can operate with clarity and confidence.
      </p>

      <div class="terminal-card max-w-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">
          <span>~/dave.engineer</span>
          <span>Terminal · Ready</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto text-sm text-cyan-200">$ deploy focus --axis leadership --axis ai-governance --axis delivery
