&gt; outcome: trusted systems, aligned teams, real momentum
</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-cyan-500/60 bg-cyan-500/15 px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-100 transition hover:border-cyan-400 hover:bg-cyan-500/25" href="/blog/">
          <span>Read Field Notes</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </a>
        <a class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-fuchsia-400/60 bg-fuchsia-500/10 px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fuchsia-100 transition hover:border-fuchsia-300 hover:bg-fuchsia-500/20" href="/work/">
          <span>See the Work</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-slate-400">01 · Leadership</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Operating cadence that unlocks teams.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-slate-400">02 · Intelligence</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Responsible AI woven into strategy &amp; delivery.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-slate-400">03 · Systems</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Platform thinking, reliable foundations, real outcomes.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="relative flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
      <div class="absolute -left-10 top-10 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/30 blur-[120px] sm:-left-16" data-parallax-depth="0.22"></div>
      <div class="relative flex h-[420px] w-full max-w-[420px] items-center justify-center">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-[3rem] border border-cyan-500/40 opacity-40" data-parallax-depth="0.25"></div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-fuchsia-400/30 opacity-30" data-parallax-depth="0.3"></div>
        <div id="hero-3d" class="relative aspect-square w-full max-w-[380px] rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-950/70 shadow-2xl shadow-cyan-500/30"></div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 w-[220px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full border border-emerald-400/60 bg-emerald-500/10 px-5 py-2 text-center font-mono text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-200" data-parallax-depth="0.18">
          Vector space: leadership × ai × trust
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <section class="relative mt-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-cyan-500/60 to-transparent opacity-50" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="diagonal-panel">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_minmax(0,1fr)] lg:items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-400">Operating Principles</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Depth in technology, empathy in leadership, clarity in outcomes.</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
            From transit technology to fintech compliance, I guide teams through complex problem spaces. We build tight feedback loops, integrate AI responsibly, and deliver software ecosystems that stay resilient long after launch day.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4">
          <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-200">System Rhythm</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">Adaptive rituals, reliable flow, and instrumentation that makes progress visible.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-200">Human Interface</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">Psychological safety, inclusive collaboration, and vibrant engineering culture.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glow-card" data-tilt>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-fuchsia-200">Strategic Mesh</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">Cross-functional alignment, intelligent automation, and governance you can trust.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% set hasFeaturedWork = false %}
  {% for item in collections.workItems %}
    {% if item.data.featured %}
      {% set hasFeaturedWork = true %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% if hasFeaturedWork %}
  <section class="mt-32 space-y-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-400">Featured Work</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Case studies from the systems desk.</h2>
      </div>
      <a class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-700/60 px-5 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-200 transition hover:border-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-200" href="/work/">
        <span>View Full Archive</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      {% for item in collections.workItems %}
        {% if item.data.featured %}
      <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.75rem] border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-950/70 p-10 shadow-xl transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-cyan-400/70">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/15 via-transparent to-fuchsia-500/20"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-400">{{ item.data.role or "Systems" }}</p>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-emerald-400/40 bg-emerald-500/10 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-200">In Flight</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">
            <a class="transition hover:text-cyan-200" href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          {% if item.data.description %}
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">{{ item.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-[0.7rem]">
            <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/60 px-4 py-2 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-100 transition hover:border-cyan-300 hover:text-cyan-50" href="{{ item.url }}">
              Deep Dive
            </a>
            {% if item.data.websiteUrl %}
            <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-fuchsia-400/60 px-4 py-2 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fuchsia-100 transition hover:border-fuchsia-300 hover:text-fuchsia-50" href="{{ item.data.websiteUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              Visit Site
              <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
            </a>
            {% endif %}
            {% if item.data.githubUrl %}
            <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-700/60 px-4 py-2 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-200 transition hover:border-cyan-300 hover:text-cyan-100" href="{{ item.data.githubUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              View Source
              <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
            </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <section class="mt-32">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-400">Signal Boost</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Find me around the web.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-sm text-slate-400">Prefer a quick DM, a detailed memo, or a pair-programming jam session? Pick the channel that fits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <a href="https://github.com/dave1010" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group glow-card flex flex-col gap-4" data-tilt>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <img src="/img/Github_black.png" alt="GitHub Icon" width="40" height="40" class="shrink-0">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">GitHub</h3>
          </div>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-2xl text-cyan-200 transition duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Explore experiments, tooling, and long-running infrastructure projects.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave1010/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group glow-card flex flex-col gap-4" data-tilt>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <img src="/img/LinkedIN_black.png" alt="LinkedIn Icon" width="40" height="40" class="shrink-0">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">LinkedIn</h3>
          </div>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-2xl text-cyan-200 transition duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-1">↗</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Let's collaborate on the next engineering leap or talk about resilient teams.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="https://twitter.com/dave1010" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group glow-card flex flex-col gap-4" data-tilt>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <img src="/img/Twitter_black.png" alt="Twitter Icon" width="40" height="40" class="shrink-0">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Twitter</h3>
          </div>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-2xl text-cyan-200 transition duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-1">~</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Occasional threads on strategy, AI, leadership craft, and playful prototypes.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
